{"tid":175897,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[投票統計]有無人日日要對住憎既人?","createTime":"2017-03-27T20:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T21:56:23.000Z","uid":27793,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9274b7928d5a495186c5672edd4e9b1e3206e819","tid":175897,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T20:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無<br />\n<br />\n我同阿嫲互憎⋯ 同住中 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b65928f775bc4b9824df950481cac457ce31c8f","tid":175897,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T20:46:42.000Z","msg":"佛家講既人生八苦：<br />\n老苦，病苦，死苦，<br />\n愛別離苦，<span style=\"color: red;\">怨憎會苦</span>，<br />\n求不得苦，五陰熾盛苦（以上既哭交集一齊受既苦）<br />\n<br />\n其中一苦：怨憎會苦真係無__錯<br />\n憎一個人已經很辛苦 仲要日日對住 人都癲"},{"pid":"1f3d8723f2d4f847b9dc0f112c9b770c2a96dc6c","tid":175897,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T21:10:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佛家講既人生八苦：<br />\n老苦，病苦，死苦，<br />\n愛別離苦，<span style=\"color: red;\">怨憎會苦</span>，<br />\n求不得苦，五陰熾盛苦（以上既哭交集一齊受既苦）<br />\n<br />\n其中一苦：怨憎會苦真係無__錯<br />\n憎一個人已經很辛苦 仲要日日對住 人都癲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係五陰熾盛苦係第七<br />\n然後第八係七個加埋？"},{"pid":"03cec4dd73b17636d891f4b4b99a44136c6a03c0","tid":175897,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T21:11:21.000Z","msg":"差唔多憎晒身邊所有既人<br />\n每日都好痛苦"},{"pid":"06717ce67489debf6a1711d3b721ef6b9a03cd7a","tid":175897,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T21:52:12.000Z","msg":"生苦，<br />\n老苦，<br />\n病苦，<br />\n死苦，<br />\n愛別離苦，<br />\n怨憎會苦，<br />\n求不得苦，<br />\n五陰熾盛苦。前七苦皆由五陰領受、聚集，故稱五陰熾盛苦。<br />\n其中五陰為<br />\n<br />\n「色」、<br />\n「受」、<br />\n「想」、<br />\n「行」、<br />\n「識」，<br />\n五陰熾盛實為其餘七苦的根源」[8]。<br />\n<br />\n梵文（Dukkha），漢傳佛教一般譯為「苦」，或者「苦諦」，從梵文語義學上來說，是表示「不安的」，「心神不寧」的意思。可對應為現代描述的「痛苦」、「悲傷」、「焦慮」、「不滿」、「沮喪」等感情。"},{"pid":"52a076a0aab4ed603817becef85086e0c66c6a04","tid":175897,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T21:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>差唔多憎晒身邊所有既人<br />\n每日都好痛苦</blockquote><br />\n所有又誇張左啲<br />\n屋企人對你唔好？"},{"pid":"08db343a103eb83d3b9a573a5d88fcdb4ee0eaa2","tid":175897,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T21:54:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>差唔多憎晒身邊所有既人<br />\n每日都好痛苦</blockquote><br />\n所有又誇張左啲<br />\n屋企人對你唔好？</blockquote><br />\n除左老豆，不過好少見佢成日唔喺屋企"},{"pid":"62b2d2712650d806003e1a1c9bf3ee809474ff81","tid":175897,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T21:56:23.000Z","msg":"每日照鏡都見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}